  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/b97dda049268813d36b5db64d9cf56d7.poster.avif?t=1738216938\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/b97dda049268813d36b5db64d9cf56d7.webm?t=1738216938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/b97dda049268813d36b5db64d9cf56d7.mp4?t=1738216938\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Prepare for intense action in \"Ninja Monkey,\" where you take control of an agile ninja monkey in an epic battle against swarms of deadly bees! This thrilling roguelike platformer takes you on a journey of survival, strategy, and ninja skills, where every decision counts.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><br><strong>⚔️ Frenetic Battles:</strong><br><br>Face relentless waves of fierce bees in a stunning sidescroll platform setting. Survive each round and choose from three exclusive upgrades to strengthen your ninja monkey and prepare for the next challenges.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/233faffc58c721a2f7600fe33324165c.poster.avif?t=1738216938\" width=616 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/233faffc58c721a2f7600fe33324165c.webm?t=1738216938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/233faffc58c721a2f7600fe33324165c.mp4?t=1738216938\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>💥 Challenge Bosses:</strong><br><br>Test your skills against formidable bosses that require advanced strategies and quick reflexes. Defeat them to advance and discover new rewards and secrets.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/9be169b62bb419a342a12ad5e6f8861b.poster.avif?t=1738216938\" width=616 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/9be169b62bb419a342a12ad5e6f8861b.webm?t=1738216938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/9be169b62bb419a342a12ad5e6f8861b.mp4?t=1738216938\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>🔄 Progression and Upgrades:</strong><br><br>Unlock a variety of upgrades, classes, maps, weapons, and abilities along your journey. Each choice shapes your ninja monkey's build, allowing unique combinations and personalized gameplay.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/afdb4b21fa660ef71c80ca47f79405af.poster.avif?t=1738216938\" width=616 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/afdb4b21fa660ef71c80ca47f79405af.webm?t=1738216938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/afdb4b21fa660ef71c80ca47f79405af.mp4?t=1738216938\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>🗺️ Game Modes:</strong><br><br>Explore different maps, each with its own challenges and environments. Face 100 rounds on each map, increasing difficulty and enemy diversity as you progress.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/f5cab88653c050ae7c07356aab907403.poster.avif?t=1738216938\" width=616 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/f5cab88653c050ae7c07356aab907403.webm?t=1738216938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/f5cab88653c050ae7c07356aab907403.mp4?t=1738216938\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>🤸‍♂️ Platforming Skills:</strong><br><br>With automatic attacks, focus on mastering platforming skills and avoiding deadly hazards. Jump, run, and dodge to survive the chaos of the bees.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/af718b13a5368ce3bb4f69449d8105ab.poster.avif?t=1738216938\" width=616 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/af718b13a5368ce3bb4f69449d8105ab.webm?t=1738216938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/af718b13a5368ce3bb4f69449d8105ab.mp4?t=1738216938\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>🎮 Addictive Gameplay:</strong><br><br>With smooth and addictive gameplay mechanics, \"Ninja Monkey\" offers an exciting and rewarding experience for all types of players. Enhance your skills, customize your build, and fight to become the ultimate ninja monkey.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/7a4969701f6557cfe758708e99f0cafa.poster.avif?t=1738216938\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/7a4969701f6557cfe758708e99f0cafa.webm?t=1738216938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Get Ready for Battle:</strong></h2><br>\"Ninja Monkey\" is more than a platformer—it's a test of your strategic skills and quick reflexes. Are you ready for the challenge? Join the fight, defeat swarms of bees, and prove your worth as the most powerful ninja monkey of all time!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Add to Your Wishlist Now!</strong></h2><br>Don't miss the chance to embark on this epic adventure. Add \"Ninja Monkey\" to your wishlist on Steam and be among the first to experience the electrifying action when the game launches!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/b97dda049268813d36b5db64d9cf56d7.poster.avif?t=1738216938\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/b97dda049268813d36b5db64d9cf56d7.webm?t=1738216938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/b97dda049268813d36b5db64d9cf56d7.mp4?t=1738216938\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Prepare for intense action in \"Ninja Monkey,\" where you take control of an agile ninja monkey in an epic battle against swarms of deadly bees! This thrilling roguelike platformer takes you on a journey of survival, strategy, and ninja skills, where every decision counts.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><br><strong>⚔️ Frenetic Battles:</strong><br><br>Face relentless waves of fierce bees in a stunning sidescroll platform setting. Survive each round and choose from three exclusive upgrades to strengthen your ninja monkey and prepare for the next challenges.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/233faffc58c721a2f7600fe33324165c.poster.avif?t=1738216938\" width=616 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/233faffc58c721a2f7600fe33324165c.webm?t=1738216938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047740/extras/233faffc58c721a2f7600fe33324165c.mp4?t=1738216938\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>💥 Challenge Bosses:</strong><br><br>Test your skills against formidable bosses that require advanced strategies and quick r